014package org.gbif.api.model.occurrence.search;
015
016import org.gbif.api.model.common.search.SearchParameter;
017
018import java.util.Date;
019
020/**
021 * Query parameters used internally (not part of the public API) to support complex data types.
022 */
023public enum InternalOccurrenceSearchParameter implements SearchParameter {
024
025  EVENT_DATE_GTE(Date.class),
026  EVENT_DATE_LTE(Date.class);
027
028  private final Class<?> type;
029
030  InternalOccurrenceSearchParameter(Class<?> type) {
031    this.type = type;
032  }
033
034  /**
035   * @return the data type expected for the value of the respective search parameter
036   */
037  @Override
038  public Class<?> type() {
039    return type;
040  }
041}
